    • Method Detail

      • canExtractChainCall

        boolean canExtractChainCall(PsiMethodCallExpression call,
                            PsiExpression expression,
                            PsiType expressionType)
        Returns true if the mapping chain call can be extracted from lambda passed to the given call.
        Parameters:
        call - call to check
        expression - expression to extract
        expressionType - resulting type of the extracted expression
        Returns:
        true if this extractor can create a mapping step from given expression

      • buildChainCall

        default java.lang.String buildChainCall(PsiVariable variable,
                                        PsiExpression expression,
                                        PsiType expressionType)
        Returns chain call string representation (starting from "." like .map(x -> x.getName())).
        Parameters:
        variable - variable to be used as chain call input
        expression - mapping expression
        expressionType - target expression type
        Returns:
        chain call. Result is correct only if canExtractChainCall(com.intellij.psi.PsiMethodCallExpression, com.intellij.psi.PsiExpression, com.intellij.psi.PsiType) was checked before for given expression and expressionType

      • getMethodName

        java.lang.String getMethodName(PsiVariable variable,
                               PsiExpression expression,
                               PsiType expressionType)
        Returns a name of the method to be extracted
        Parameters:
        variable - variable to be used as chain call input
        expression - mapping expression
        expressionType - target expression type
        Returns:
        chain call. Result is correct only if canExtractChainCall(com.intellij.psi.PsiMethodCallExpression, com.intellij.psi.PsiExpression, com.intellij.psi.PsiType) was checked before for given expression and expressionType

      • fixCallName

        default java.lang.String fixCallName(PsiMethodCallExpression call,
                                     PsiType newElementType)
        Returns new name for the existing call from which element is to be extracted. Sometimes it should be renamed depending on the new element type (e.g. map to mapToObj).
        Parameters:
        call - call to fix the name
        newElementType - new element type (to be passed as lambda parameter)
        Returns:
        new call name. Default implementation returns current name.
